{"tid":2268864,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼聯傳奇傑斯，嘔打女友被捕","createTime":"2020-11-03T06:16:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T12:00:17.000Z","uid":34571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dd19d54716822ff70348534b0f57f032371bf31f","tid":2268864,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T06:16:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20201103/I62VXUZZTVHJDFWERSA23I5DZY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20201103%2FI62VXUZZTVHJDFWERSA23I5DZY%2F&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0Evhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=713d3b28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20201103%2FI62VXUZZTVHJDFWERSA23I5DZY%2F&h=55b67e2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20201103/I62VXUZZTVHJDFWERSA23I5DZY/</a><br />\n報道指出，周日晚上10時後，傑斯位於英格蘭沃斯利價值1,700萬鎊（約1.7億港元）的豪宅發生爭吵聲，當地警方接報到場處理，結果現年46歲的傑斯，因涉嫌對他人身體造成實質傷害被捕。<br />\n曼徹斯特警察局發言人表示：「周日晚上10時05分，警方接到襲擊報告，一名30多歲的婦女受輕傷，不需要接受任何治療，一名46歲男子因涉嫌第47條襲擊和第39條普通襲擊罪被捕。」警方續指，被捕男子已經保釋，案件正等待調查。"},{"pid":"9563681ee77f10b81cb543e7e34f5c72d51f9c70","tid":2268864,"uid":201601,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T06:18:18.000Z","msg":"傑斯性格係咁，無計"},{"pid":"2633114271b9ca9b69aeb0c9f801664c516279b1","tid":2268864,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T06:20:22.000Z","msg":"用嘔吐物打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n毆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb915973e67260b9b9188919d3483074491827f","tid":2268864,"uid":64484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T06:22:21.000Z","msg":"魔性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf9bd2cf83b39d39b872e7a417ebc36837b1194","tid":2268864,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2633114271b9ca9b69aeb